ROGAN: "Meanwhile, he saved those astronauts trapped in space. You didn't hear a peep."

RODGERS: "And what he does when there are natural disasters with Starlink."

ROGAN: "He's revolutionizing space travel and satellite internet availability all over the world."

RODGERS: "And saving billions of your tax money from funding stupid programs all over the world."

ROGAN: "He said billions were sent out with no receipts at all. He said if this was a public company, they would be delisted and all the executives would be thrown in prison. But in the government it's just business as usual."

